sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant MW as Llama Stack<br/>Middleware Chain<br/>8321/TCP
    participant Auth as OAuth2/JWKS<br/>Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Quota as QuotaMiddleware<br/>(SQLite KV)
    participant Router as API Router<br/>(Dynamic Routes)
    participant ABAC as ABAC Engine<br/>(Cedar-like)
    participant Inference as Inference Provider<br/>(Router)
    participant VLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8000/TCP
    participant RAG as RAG Tool Runtime
    participant VectorDB as Vector DB<br/>(pgvector :5432)
    participant Safety as Safety Shield<br/>(Inline)
    participant Tool as Tool Runtime<br/>(Web Search/MCP)

    Note over Client, VLLM: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request
    Client->>MW: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>HTTP/HTTPS :8321<br/>Bearer Token (JWT)
    MW->>Auth: Validate JWT (JWKS fetch)<br/>HTTPS :443 TLS 1.2+
    Auth-->>MW: Token Valid + Claims
    MW->>Quota: Check rate limit<br/>100/day anon, 1000/day auth
    Quota-->>MW: Allowed
    MW->>Router: Route to inference handler
    Router->>ABAC: Evaluate access rules
    ABAC-->>Router: Permitted
    Router->>Inference: chat_completion(request)
    Inference->>VLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS :8000<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    VLLM-->>Inference: SSE stream chunks
    Inference-->>MW: SSE stream
    MW-->>Client: text/event-stream<br/>x-trace-id header

    Note over Client, VectorDB: Flow 2: RAG Query (Vector IO + Inference)
    Client->>MW: POST /v1/tool-runtime/rag-tool/query<br/>HTTP/HTTPS :8321<br/>Bearer Token
    MW->>Auth: Validate JWT
    Auth-->>MW: Valid
    MW->>Router: Route to RAG handler
    Router->>RAG: rag_query(request)
    RAG->>Inference: Generate embeddings<br/>(inline or remote)
    Inference-->>RAG: Embedding vectors
    RAG->>VectorDB: Query similar chunks<br/>PostgreSQL :5432<br/>Optional TLS, Password auth
    VectorDB-->>RAG: Relevant chunks
    RAG->>Inference: Generate response with context<br/>HTTP :8000 → vLLM
    Inference->>VLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(with RAG context)
    VLLM-->>Inference: Response
    Inference-->>RAG: LLM response
    RAG-->>MW: Final response
    MW-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client, Tool: Flow 3: Agent Turn with Tool Execution
    Client->>MW: POST /v1/agents/{id}/session/{sid}/turn<br/>HTTP/HTTPS :8321 (SSE)<br/>Bearer Token
    MW->>Auth: Validate JWT
    Auth-->>MW: Valid
    MW->>Router: Route to agent handler
    Router->>Inference: Initial LLM call<br/>HTTP :8000 → vLLM
    Inference->>VLLM: Chat completion
    VLLM-->>Inference: Tool call response
    Router->>Safety: Run safety shield<br/>(in-process)
    Safety-->>Router: Safe
    Router->>Tool: Execute tool<br/>HTTPS :443 (Tavily/Brave)<br/>API key auth
    Tool-->>Router: Tool results
    Router->>Inference: Final LLM call with tool results
    Inference->>VLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions
    VLLM-->>Inference: Final response (SSE)
    Inference-->>Router: Stream chunks
    Router-->>MW: SSE stream
    MW-->>Client: text/event-stream<br/>x-trace-id header
